<LEADPARA>  Dozens of dahlias; East Bay Dahlia Society will host a show Saturday and
Sunday at Lakeside Garden Center, 666 Bellevue Ave., Oakland. Hours: 1:30 to 5
p.m. Saturday, 10 a.m. to 5 p.m. Sunday. At the same time the Dahlia Trial
